{"ts": "2026-07-13T01:44:15.268+00:00", "event": "request", "attempt": 1, "n_messages": 1, "roles": ["user"], "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Build a **desktop environment** in a single self-contained HTML file — visually\ninspired by Ubuntu (dark theme, top bar or dock, desktop wallpaper area,\ndraggable-looking windows). Polish matters, but the following contract is what\ngets graded, exactly as specified — element IDs and behaviors must match:\n\n**Shell**\n- `#desktop` — the desktop root element, filling the browser viewport.\n- `#taskbar` — a taskbar/dock containing two launcher buttons:\n  `#open-files` and `#open-notepad`.\n- App windows must open at a **usable size — at least 360×240 CSS pixels** —\n  with their content visible, not collapsed or zero-height.\n- Clicking a launcher shows its window: `#files-window` / `#notepad-window`.\n  Each window has a close button with class `.win-close` that hides it\n  (display none or removed from view). Windows can be reopened any number of\n  times.\n\n**Files app** (a browsable replica of a Linux filesystem — static fake data)\n- `#files-path` shows the current absolute path, starting at `/`.\n- Every file/folder in the listing is an element with class `.fs-item`; its\n  visible text is the entry name.\n- The root `/` must contain at least: `bin`, `etc`, `home`, `usr`, `var`.\n- `/home` contains `user`; `/home/user` contains at least `Documents`,\n  `Downloads`, `Pictures` (plus any files you like).\n- **Double-clicking** a folder navigates into it (path updates); `#files-up`\n  navigates to the parent. Deeper structure beyond the required paths is\n  welcome.\n\n**Notepad app** (tabbed, persistent)\n- `#tabs` holds the tab strip; each tab is an element with class `.tab`.\n- `#new-tab` creates a new empty tab and makes it active.\n- `#editor` is a `<textarea>` showing the active tab's content; clicking a\n  `.tab` switches to it.\n- All tabs and their content **persist in `localStorage`**: closing the\n  notepad window and reopening it — or reloading the whole page — restores\n  every tab and its text exactly.\n\nSingle file, all CSS/JS inline, no external resources, no frameworks required\n(vanilla JS is fine). Every control must actually work — no dead UI, no stub\nfunctions, no placeholder features. Ship it complete.\n\n\nRespond with a single fenced ```html code block containing the complete contents of app.html — one fully self-contained file with all CSS and JavaScript inline. No external resources (no CDNs, fonts, or images). Do not include anything outside the code block."}]}
{"ts": "2026-07-13T01:44:41.035+00:00", "event": "response", "attempt": 1, "text": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>Ubuntu‑like Desktop</title>\n<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  html, body { height: 100%; width: 100%; overflow: hidden; font-family: Ubuntu, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif; background: #1e1e1e; color: #e0e0e0; }\n  #desktop { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c2c2c 0%, #1a1a1a 100%); }\n  /* Taskbar / Dock */\n  #taskbar { position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); display: flex; gap: 8px; padding: 8px 16px; background: rgba(30,30,30,0.9); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border-top: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0; z-index: 1000; }\n  #taskbar button { background: #333; border: none; color: #e0e0e0; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; transition: background 0.2s; }\n  #taskbar button:hover { background: #444; }\n  #taskbar button:active { background: #555; }\n  /* Window base */\n  .window { position: absolute; min-width: 360px; min-height: 240px; background: #2b2b2b; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); display: none; flex-direction: column; z-index: 100; }\n  .window-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 6px 12px; background: #333; border-bottom: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; user-select: none; cursor: default; }\n  .window-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; }\n  .win-close { background: transparent; border: none; color: #e0e0e0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1; cursor: pointer; padding: 4px; border-radius: 4px; }\n  .win-close:hover { background: #c0392b; color: #fff; }\n  .window-content { flex: 1; overflow: auto; padding: 12px; }\n  /* Files app */\n  #files-path { font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 6px 10px; background: #333; border-radius: 4px; }\n  #files-up { margin-bottom: 8px; }\n  #files-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr)); gap: 8px; }\n  .fs-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding: 10px; background: #333; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s; user-select: none; }\n  .fs-item:hover { background: #3d3d3d; }\n  .fs-item.folder { color: #7aa2f7; }\n  .fs-item.file { color: #9ece6a; }\n  .fs-item-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n  .fs-item-name { font-size: 12px; text-align: center; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; width: 100%; }\n  /* Notepad app */\n  #tabs { display: flex; gap: 2px; margin-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #444; padding-bottom: 2px; }\n  .tab { padding: 6px 12px; background: #333; border: 1px solid #444; border-bottom: none; border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; color: #b0b0b0; transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s; }\n  .tab:hover { background: #3a3a3a; color: #e0e0e0; }\n  .tab.active { background: #2b2b2b; color: #e0e0e0; border-color: #444; }\n  #new-tab { padding: 6px 10px; background: #333; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 6px; color: #e0e0e0; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; }\n  #new-tab:hover { background: #3a3a3a; }\n  #editor { width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 200px; background: #1e1e1e; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 4px; color: #d0d0d0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; padding: 10px; resize: none; outline: none; }\n  #editor:focus { border-color: #7aa2f7; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div id=\"desktop\">\n  <div id=\"taskbar\">\n    <button id=\"open-files\">Files</button>\n    <button id=\"open-notepad\">Notepad</button>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Files Window -->\n  <div id=\"files-window\" class=\"window\" style=\"top: 80px; left: 80px; width: 560px; height: 420px;\">\n    <div class=\"window-header\">\n      <span class=\"window-title\">Files</span>\n      <button class=\"win-close\" aria-label=\"Close\">&times;</button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"window-content\">\n      <div id=\"files-path\">/</div>\n      <button id=\"files-up\" disabled>↑ Up</button>\n      <div id=\"files-list\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Notepad Window -->\n  <div id=\"notepad-window\" class=\"window\" style=\"top: 120px; left: 140px; width: 600px; height: 460px;\">\n    <div class=\"window-header\">\n      <span class=\"window-title\">Notepad</span>\n      <button class=\"win-close\" aria-label=\"Close\">&times;</button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"window-content\" style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; height:100%;\">\n      <div id=\"tabs\"></div>\n      <button id=\"new-tab\">+ New Tab</button>\n      <textarea id=\"editor\" spellcheck=\"false\"></textarea>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n/* ---------- Filesystem data ---------- */\nconst fs = {\n  '/': {\n    type: 'folder',\n    children: {\n      bin: { type: 'folder', children: {} },\n      etc: { type: 'folder', children: {} },\n      home: {\n        type: 'folder',\n        children: {\n          user: {\n            type: 'folder',\n            children: {\n              Documents: { type: 'folder', children: {} },\n              Downloads: { type: 'folder', children: {} },\n              Pictures: { type: 'folder', children: {} },\n              'readme.txt': { type: 'file', content: 'Welcome to your home folder!' }\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      usr: { type: 'folder', children: {} },\n      var: { type: 'folder', children: {} }\n    }\n  }\n};\n\n/* ---------- State ---------- */\nlet currentPath = ['']; // root represented as empty string for easier join\nconst filesWindow = document.getElementById('files-window');\nconst notepadWindow = document.getElementById('notepad-window');\nconst filesPathEl = document.getElementById('files-path');\nconst filesUpBtn = document.getElementById('files-up');\nconst filesListEl = document.getElementById('files-list');\nconst tabsEl = document.getElementById('tabs');\nconst newTabBtn = document.getElementById('new-tab');\nconst editorEl = document.getElementById('editor');\n\n/* ---------- Helpers ---------- */\nfunction getNode(pathArray) {\n  let node = fs['/'];\n  for (let i = 1; i < pathArray.length; i++) {\n    const name = pathArray[i];\n    if (node.children && node.children[name]) {\n      node = node.children[name];\n    } else return null;\n  }\n  return node;\n}\n\nfunction renderPath() {\n  filesPathEl.textContent = currentPath.length === 1 ? '/' : '/' + currentPath.slice(1).join('/');\n  filesUpBtn.disabled = currentPath.length === 1;\n}\n\nfunction renderListing() {\n  const node = getNode(currentPath);\n  filesListEl.innerHTML = '';\n  if (!node || !node.children) return;\n  Object.entries(node.children).sort(([a],[b]) => a.localeCompare(b)).forEach(([name, entry]) => {\n    const div = document.createElement('div');\n    div.className = `fs-item ${entry.type}`;\n    div.dataset.name = name;\n    div.dataset.type = entry.type;\n    div.innerHTML = `\n      <span class=\"fs-item-icon\">${entry.type === 'folder' ? '📁' : '📄'}</span>\n      <span class=\"fs-item-name\">${name}</span>\n    `;\n    filesListEl.appendChild(div);\n  });\n}\n\n/* ---------- Files app events ---------- */\nfilesListEl.addEventListener('dblclick', e => {\n  const item = e.target.closest('.fs-item');\n  if (!item) return;\n  if (item.dataset.type === 'folder') {\n    currentPath.push(item.dataset.name);\n    renderPath();\n    renderListing();\n  }\n});\n\nfilesUpBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n  if (currentPath.length > 1) {\n    currentPath.pop();\n    renderPath();\n    renderListing();\n  }\n});\n\n/* ---------- Notepad app ---------- */\nconst STORAGE_KEY = 'notepadTabs';\nlet tabs = [];\nlet activeTabId = null;\n\nfunction loadTabs() {\n  try {\n    const data = localStorage.getItem(STORAGE_KEY);\n    if (data) {\n      tabs = JSON.parse(data);\n      if (tabs.length === 0) createTab();\n      else activeTabId = tabs[0].id;\n    } else {\n      createTab();\n    }\n  } catch (_) {\n    createTab();\n  }\n  renderTabs();\n  showActiveTab();\n}\n\nfunction saveTabs() {\n  localStorage.setItem(STORAGE_KEY, JSON.stringify(tabs));\n}\n\nfunction createTab(title = 'Untitled') {\n  const id = Date.now().toString(36) + Math.random().toString(36).substr(2,5);\n  const tab = { id, title, content: '' };\n  tabs.push(tab);\n  activeTabId = id;\n  saveTabs();\n  return tab;\n}\n\nfunction renderTabs() {\n  tabsEl.innerHTML = '';\n  tabs.forEach(tab => {\n    const btn = document.createElement('button');\n    btn.className = 'tab' + (tab.id === activeTabId ? ' active' : '');\n    btn.dataset.id = tab.id;\n    btn.textContent = tab.title;\n    btn.addEventListener('click', () => switchTab(tab.id));\n    tabsEl.appendChild(btn);\n  });\n}\n\nfunction switchTab(id) {\n  // save current editor content to active tab before switching\n  const current = tabs.find(t => t.id === activeTabId);\n  if (current) {\n    current.content = editorEl.value;\n  }\n  activeTabId = id;\n  saveTabs();\n  renderTabs();\n  showActiveTab();\n}\n\nfunction showActiveTab() {\n  const tab = tabs.find(t => t.id === activeTabId);\n  if (tab) {\n    editorEl.value = tab.content;\n  } else {\n    editorEl.value = '';\n  }\n}\n\neditorEl.addEventListener('input', () => {\n  const tab = tabs.find(t => t.id === activeTabId);\n  if (tab) {\n    tab.content = editorEl.value;\n    saveTabs();\n  }\n});\n\nnewTabBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n  const tab = createTab(`Untitled ${tabs.length + 1}`);\n  renderTabs();\n  showActiveTab();\n});\n\n/* ---------- Window management ---------- */\nfunction showWindow(win) {\n  win.style.display = 'flex';\n  // bring to front\n  win.style.zIndex = ++topZ;\n}\nlet topZ = 200;\n\ndocument.getElementById('open-files').addEventListener('click', () => {\n  showWindow(filesWindow);\n  renderPath();\n  renderListing();\n});\n\ndocument.getElementById('open-notepad').addEventListener('click', () => {\n  showWindow(notepadWindow);\n  if (tabs.length === 0) loadTabs(); // ensure loaded once\n});\n\ndocument.querySelectorAll('.win-close').forEach(btn => {\n  btn.addEventListener('click', e => {\n    e.target.closest('.window').style.display = 'none';\n  });\n});\n\n/* ---------- Initial load ---------- */\nloadTabs(); // load notepad data immediately so it's ready\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>", "stop_reason": "stop", "tokens_in": 623, "tokens_out": 3867, "total_ms": 25766.7, "ttft_ms": 858.0, "cost_usd": 0, "served_by": "Nvidia", "tool_calls": []}
